        "created_at": "2025-05-19T19:04:56.310Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Signal only supports Debian and Debian-based distros.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Confirm that your OS supports Signal Desktop:</li>\n<li>Windows 10 and 11.</li>\n<li>macOS 11 (Big Sur) and above.</li>\n<li>Linux 64-bit distributions supporting APT, like Ubuntu or Debian.</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p>From the support article: <a href=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/en-us/articles/360008216551-Installing-Signal#install_desktop\">https://support.signal.org/hc/en-us/articles/360008216551-Installing-Signal#install_desktop</a></p>",
